      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's not even about the mundane stuff though. its more like... looking at a map and realizing you're at the edge of the world. there are no more roads to take. i feel like i've reached the end of my personal route and there's just nothing beyond this point. no more destinations, no more connections. just a blank space where the path should be.",
